events.name: Eminem
events.info: Please note there is a strict ticket limit on these events. Orders associated with the same name, e-mail address, billing address, credit card number or other information will be cancelled.
events.pleaseNote: AGE RESTRICTIONS: No under 14s standing on pitch. All under 16s have to be accompanied by an adult and babes in arms are strongly discouraged. Seats located in U1-U51 Upper Tier are not recommended for those who have a fear of heights. Please click to read Twickenham Stadium's Ground Rules Plus Special Guests: 2 Chainz, Royce 5'9", Boogie

venues.name: Twickenham Stadium

boxOfficeInfo.phoneNumberDetail: Ticketmaster UK: 0844 847 2492 International: 00 44 161 385 1420 Calls will cost 7 ppm plus your network access charge.
boxOfficeInfo.willCallDetail: The RFU Ticket Office is located in the South East corner of the Stadium (on the corner of Whitton and Rugby Road) The ticket office will open on the day of the event for collections. Opening hours vary. Please check the relevant event page at www.rfu.com/Tickets for times. PLEASE NOTE ALL TICKETS NEED TO BE COLLECTED AT LEAST 45 MINUTES PRIOR TO KICK OFF. Please take your credit/debit card used to make the booking and your Ticketmaster Booking Reference number.

venues.parkingDetail: Full details of parking at Twickenham can be found at www.rfu.com/TwickenhamStadium/Parking.
venues.accessibleSeatingDetail: Rolling Stones-June 2018 For further Accessible Ticketing information,please call 0203 325 8999. Eminem-14-July 2018 Please call 0208 831 6666 and callers should select option 4. All other events: ----------------- www.englandrugby.com/tickets - accessibility forms can be found under the About Tickets section Email address: disabledaccess@therfu.com Telephone Number: 0208 831 6666 (option 4)

generalInfo.generalRule: No video cameras or recording devices allowed
generalInfo.childRule: All children aged 2-5 years old should be seated with their responsible adult in the enclosures or lower tiers. Upper Tiers are not deemed to be suitable for children under the age of 8 years old. All children must be accompanied by an adult. Babes in arms and children under 2 years old are permitted only once permission has been issued by the RFU. They do not require a match ticket but are only permitted to be sat with their responsible adult in the lower tier or enclosure areas. Children Rules for New York Giants v St Louis Rams. Child Prices are available for Children aged 16 and under. All children must be accompanied by an Adult. Maximum of 3 Children per Adult. Babes in arms and children under 18 months old are permitted only once permission has been issued by Twickenham. They do not require a match ticket but are only permitted to be sat with their responsible adult
